[size=24]Welcome everyone to Limited-X![/size]
This server has 90% no lag and runs without Hamachi! It is a 1.6.6 Minecraft Bukkit server. Its brand new and unfinished. If you join and help build the upcoming town it's very likely of you becoming a Moderator.
[align=center]Heres the IP so you don't miss it. [/align]
[align=center][size=36]96.244.178.211[/size][/align]
The point of this server is basically real life, without jobs.
You own your own shop, that you will make.
[align=center]~~~~~~~~The ranks~~~~~~~~[/align] [align=center]Immigrant (Start out) Citizen (Build a sign for a starting house in spawn) Journeyman (Build your own house in the development) Mayor (Build a town) Governor (Control an entire city of towns) Vice President - ur_mom_in_HD (good friend) President - made4speed2 (me)[/align]
EXPECT MORE RANKS TO BE COMING SOON!
